{
  "chapter": 66,
  "chapter_summary": "赵雅带项少龙（扮董匡）前往藏军谷勘察牧场选址，项少龙故意以粗鄙言行令赵雅反感。回到邯郸后，赵穆邀项少龙赴侯府密议，商讨刺杀廉颇、李牧以篡夺赵国君位的计划，项少龙假意应承。宴前一名女刺客行刺赵穆，项少龙挡下毒匕首救了赵穆一命，同时放走刺客。宴会上乐乘、郭开告知大才女纪嫣然将出席，项少龙激动不已。花园中他偶遇旧情人田贞，被她认出声音，承诺日后带走她们姊妹。项少龙偷听赵穆与赵雅对话，得知赵穆欲以赵雅笼络自己。最后他在凉亭以哲理之言打动赵雅，使她对他产生好感。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！你若以刚才那种神态语气和赵雅说话，迟早会给她看穿底细。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董匡是出名只懂养马的人，其他方面则是粗人一个，你自己斟酌看看吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "他奶奶的，夫人怎知有这么一处好地方？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_fa",
      "speaker_name": "谢法",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此地名藏军谷，唯一的入口是刚才的一线天，当年我大赵的武灵王与戎狄作战，曾藏军于此，以奇兵得胜，自此后这处便命名为藏军谷，董先生认为还可以吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呀！真是要操他的娘！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_fa",
      "text": "鄙人一见好东西，会忍不住要说几句操他娘。这么美好的地方，不是更要大操他的娘吗？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_fa",
      "speaker_name": "谢法",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "如此说，先生是否要选此谷作牧场呢？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "唔！这地方甚合鄙人眼缘，由今天开始，藏军谷就是鄙人建立第一个牧场的地方，他奶奶的！想不到这么顺利便拣到场址。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董先生既找到理想的场址，可以回去了吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "鄙人还要仔细勘察这里的水源、泥土和草质，他奶奶的，夫人这么急着赶回去做啥？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我还有约会，哪来时间多陪先生呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "未知是谁令夫人这么急着回去？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这是我的事，与先生半点关系都没有。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听说你把赵雅气得半死，怎么了？对这荡妇没有兴趣吗？现在的她比任何时候更易弄上手呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "我怕她是孝成王的奸细，哪敢惹她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是否奸细，谁比我更清楚？若对她有意，我自会给你安排。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "那件事侯爷想过没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "现在邯郸，谁不是我的亲信，只要能除去几个人，我必可安稳地坐上赵国君主之位。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "首先要杀的两个人是廉颇和李牧吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有你这种人才助我，何愁大业不成，不过这两人身旁猛将如云，恐怕很难下手。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "若是容易，侯爷早下手了，这事可包在我身上，只要我能得到他们的精确情报，必能一击成功。听说现在他们都不在邯郸，最好有方法把他们召回来，我使人做好埋伏，干手净脚把他们干掉。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你真的如此有把握？这两人只是家将亲兵足有数千人，相当不易对付。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "没有人比我更精刺杀之术，侯爷放心好了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事须从长计议才成，你最好先建牧场，打下根基，这方面有我在孝成王跟前说项，定可顺利达到。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "鄙人全听侯爷吩咐，这也是君上的指示。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "孝成王现在对你印象绝佳，但记着牧场的事要加紧进行。哈！你这一招命中赵人的要害，没有比赵人更需要你这救星了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "来吧！客人也应该来了，今晚请来的除了几个在邯郸最有权势的人外，还有为东周君的事来此的各国使节，趁这机会见见他们吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看上她吗？此女叫赵致，父亲是赵国有德行学问的大儒，师父则是剑术大家，我也拿她没有办法。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今趟幸有你在，否则吾命难保。哼！那些人全是酒囊饭桶，给刺客潜进来仍一无所知。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_le_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "乐乘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今天我是左右做人难，在邯郸所有自认有点头面的人，都争着来参加今晚的宴会，但席位却是有限，唉……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_kai",
      "speaker_name": "郭开",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我也遇到同样的难题，惟有把责任全推到侯爷身上，教他们直接向侯爷询问，为何没有被列于邀请名单上。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_le_cheng",
      "text": "今晚的宴会为何如此热闹？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_le_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "乐乘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "侯爷没有告诉先生吗？与秦国寡妇清齐名的大才女纪嫣然来邯郸作客，侯爷本没有把握将她邀来，岂知她毫不犹豫答应，累得所有人都要挤到这里来，好一睹她的风采。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_kai",
      "speaker_name": "郭开",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "哈！想不到董先生是另一个'才女迷'！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "田贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "对不起！奴家认错人哩！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_zhen",
      "text": "没有关系！你叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "田贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你真是项爷，奴家发梦也记得你那难忘的声音。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "田贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "奴家死也忘不掉你，我们都不知多么为你担心呢！现在大爷没事，多谢老天爷哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_zhen",
      "text": "现在我的真正身份是个大秘密……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "田贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "奴家明白，就算死都不会泄露大爷身份。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_zhen",
      "text": "连妹子也不可透露此事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "田贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好吧！不过她亦像奴家般思念大爷呢！",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_zhen",
      "text": "只要你乖乖地听话，我会把你们姊妹带走，绝不食言。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要说了，我怎也不会去陪那种粗鄙不文的莽夫，你手上多的是美女，为何不拿去送他？例如你最疼爱的田家姊妹花，不是可更令他满意吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "是否你仍忘不掉项少龙呢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "不要胡言乱语，谁说我忘不了他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "不再想他自然最好，今趟若我们六国结成联盟，尽管是秦国亦难逃被瓜分的厄运，那时我要项少龙死无葬身之地，他就算死了，我也要鞭尸始可泄心头之恨。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "你有那本事才说吧！噢！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "你还不回去招待客人吗？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你不要我先招待你吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "放开我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你答应我去陪董匡，我才放开你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "你为何这么看重董匡？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "不是我看重他，而是你的王兄有命，至紧要好好笼络此人，你还不明白吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "或者他不好女色呢？否则为何昨晚他连王兄送他歌姬都拒绝了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "只要是真正的男人，谁不好色，我看是他眼光过高，看不上那些歌姬吧！我们的雅夫人怎可同日而语。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "眼光高便去追求纪嫣然，我赵雅算什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "纪嫣然是出名无情的石女，怎及得上温柔多情的赵雅，不要多说了，听说董匡走出来透透气，你帮我找他回来吧，那么紧张干嘛？又不是要你今晚便陪他入房登榻。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董先生为何离群独处？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "鄙人一向不喜热闹，看！天空多么迷人，它与我们的关系是多么密切，全靠它怀抱里的星辰，我们才可辨认路途，知道季节时间，人死了后，便会回归到它深幽之处。它象征我们最崇高的理想，冥冥中主宰着大地上每一个人的命运。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "想起无论是墨翟或孔丘，武王或周公，当他们抬起头来，看到都是同样的天空，我们怎能不感到天空的恒久长存，人类生命的渺小和短暂。可怜大多数人仍忘不掉权位之争，为眼前浅窄的利益，朝夕不让，争个你死我活，所以我董某人从来对争权夺利没有好感，只希望自由自在地养我的宝贝马儿，爱说什么就说什么！操它奶奶的天空，我实在太爱它，所以要操它，就像去操我心爱的女人那样。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今天人家冒渎先生，真不好意思。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夫人看到鄙人是怎样就怎样算了，何误会之有？就像这夜空，假若你只看一眼，可能一无所觉，但假若你定心细看，你会看到愈来愈多的星辰，愈是深黑的晚夜，每颗星辰都有它的故事。没有开始，亦没有终结。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先生的话真动听！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "好了！我也应回到那人间的俗世里，只希望时间快点过去，可趁早回家睡觉。梦中的世界，不是更美丽吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 410
    }
  ],
